show.description:
She was all set to marry the man her family had chosen — the mandap was decorated, the rituals had begun.
But just before the final vows, the wedding came to a shocking halt. In the chaos, a stranger stepped forward… and within moments, she was married to him instead.
No one knew who he was — only that he carried a quiet intensity and a past no one dared ask about. What began as a mistake soon turns into a tangled story of secrets, fate, and unexpected love.
